               COMPUTE CALCULATED-INTEREST = ACCOUNT-BALANCE * (INTEREST-RATE + .005)
           ELSE
               COMPUTE CALCULATED-INTEREST = ACCOUNT-BALANCE * INTEREST-RATE
           END-IF.

